data.description: RECENTLY APPRAISED. PRICED WELL UNDER APPRAISED VALUE! Phenomenal and expansive city & mountain views from the slope of the South Mtn preserve in this spectacular highly appointed home. Located in the luxury private gated community of Talasera,  this home offers 5 bedrooms/4.5 baths, 3 car garage. Grand entry foyer, large formal living/dining room with expansive windows allowing plenty of natural light.  Custom lighting fixtures, wood-inspired tile flooring, tray ceilings, wood beams and plenty more featured in this impeccable home. Oversized family room with gas fireplace is open to the custom kitchen w/ upscale GE SS appliances, large island/breakfast bar, dry bar/wine cooler, walk-in pantry. Resort-like backyard features a newly 2022 completed pool with heated spa, built in grill, mini green space, pool decking, fire pit and multiple seating areas. Experience the desert views--spiral staircase leads up to an observation/roof deck offering panoramic city and mountain views. Talasera is a tranquil and pristine location and only 20 minutes or less to PHX Airport and downtown PHX.   Welcome home!
